Alex Kapp Horner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alex_Kapp_Horner 0 Alex Kapp Horner (born Alexandra Kapp; December 5, 1969) is an American television actress, best recognized for her role as Lindsay on the CBS sitcom The New Adventures of Old Christine (2006–10).
